Class EraseWffsPreprocessRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • mmj.pa.PreprocessRequest

  • public class EraseWffsPreprocessRequest
extends PreprocessRequest
    EraseWffsPreprocessRequest implements a user request for an erasure operation on non-QED Derivation Step formulas in a proof text area.

    • Method Detail

      • doIt

        public java.lang.String doIt(java.lang.String proofTextArea)
                      throws ProofAsstException
        Erases formulas on non-QED Derivation Steps which contain a Ref label.

        Non-qed Derivation Steps begin in column 1 with a digit, and if the Ref is present then there must be two colons (":") in the first token and the first token must not end with a ":" (otherwise the Proof Worksheet will error out anyway.)

        Specified by:
        doIt in class PreprocessRequest
        Parameters:
        proofTextArea - Proof Worksheet text string
        Returns:
        proofTextArea modified by editing operation
        Throws:
        ProofAsstException
